data.description: Cute bungalow that has been totally redone, down to the studs. New sub-floor. 3 window units, 3 wall heaters, tiled shower, wood look flooring, gas stove, frig, covered front and back porches, large trees for plenty of shade, slab for garage or shop. Would make a great first time home or rental opportunity.
